ticket.original-body: I couldn't find any other tickets related to this so I wanted to make sure it was covered. My functional tests make use of the fixture_file_upload method which isn't representative of the new ActionDispatch::Http::UploadedFile class for uploaded files. This bit me when my code called the path method on an uploaded file: undefined method `path' for #<ActionDispatch::Http::UploadedFile:0x104233110>
